        "can_view_edit_history": true,
        "can_wiki": false,
        "cooked": "<p>I understand the identical file names cause confusion.<br>\nHowever, the parameters for different models are very diverse. Therefore, it won\u2019t be easy to figure out a way to define the naming rules.</p>",
